            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Aurelia Victorina qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <lb n="2"/>emit arca ex proprio suo <lb n="3"/>et vixit annus <note>sic</note> XLV et dies <lb n="4"/>tres et post <supplied reason="lost">o</supplied>bitum ipseius <note>sic</note> <lb n="5"/>fecit Fortunatus alonnus <note>sic</note> <lb n="6"/>ipseius <note>sic</note> ex boto <note>sic</note> ips<surplus>e</surplus>ius fecit <lb n="7"/>si quis voluerit corpus in<lb break="no" n="8"/>pon<supplied reason="lost">e</supplied>re dabit in fiscum <lb n="9"/>|(denariorum<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <expan><abbr>fol</abbr><ex>les</ex></expan> |(mille)
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Z. 4: überliefert ist POSTRITVM. Z. 6: überliefert ist DOLO IPSIIVS. Z. 9: überliefert ist POL.</p>
            </div>
